## Limitations
This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date research and the evolving nature of microbiology studies. Some sources may not reflect the latest scientific advancements, and the complexity of microbial interactions with human systems may not be fully captured. Further research is needed to explore the depth of microbial influence on human behavior and other emerging areas.

